{
  "stem": "1061.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "While we were in that villa, the Russians came.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Meaning they arrived at the villa, and they wanted to know who was living here, and who were these people were.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we told them who we are.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Halina, I think, spoke Russian also.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They said, oh great.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "You are here, that's good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We come tomorrow, you're going to be working for us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Meanwhile, there was a Russian woman among us, who also said-- she warned us that they rape women, and we better get out of here, which we did.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "The following day, we started a trek back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Because we really had no idea, now, what happened to the family, to the extended family that I told you about, Babcia Tenenblum.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew because the Russians were there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were told the war was over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we really didn't know how the was finished, who-- who fought whom and how, and whatever.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We just knew that the Russians-- we were on the German territory, inside of Germany, that was liberated by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we started going back to Poland, in the way as, as we walked.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we walked to a train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we were on the train for a day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we were thrown off the train because the Russians were going back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we sat on the, on the railroad stations.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then we got on another train, got bumped off again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Whatever it is, by the time we came back closer to Poland, we were warned by a Russian officer who turned out to be Jewish, he heard us in the train.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He asked us where we were going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we said that we were going back to Starachowice.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
